### Stage 12：AI Provider 与文章分析

@articleId = 1

### 查询 Ollama 状态
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/ai/providers
Accept: application/json

> {%
client.test("AI Provider 状态接口正常", function () {
  client.assert(response.status === 200, "预期 200");
  client.assert(response.body.data.length >= 1, "至少应有一个 Provider");
});
%}

### 使用 Ollama 分析文章
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/articles/{{articleId}}/ai/analyze?provider=ollama
Accept: application/json

> {%
client.test("AI 分析成功", function () {
  client.assert(response.status === 200, "预期 200");
  client.assert(response.body.data.status === "SUCCESS", "分析状态应为 SUCCESS");
});
%}

### 读取持久化结果
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/articles/{{articleId}}/ai
Accept: application/json
